title: Google\Cloud\LifeSciences\V2beta\Pipeline
name: Pipeline
description:
Specifies a series of actions to execute, expressed as Docker containers.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.lifesciences.v2beta.Pipeline

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.actions
params.description: The list of actions to execute, in the order they are specified.

params.name: data.environment
params.description: The environment to pass into every action. Each action can also specify additional environment variables but cannot delete an entry from this map (though they can overwrite it with a different value).

params.name: data.timeout
params.description: The maximum amount of time to give the pipeline to complete. This includes the time spent waiting for a worker to be allocated. If the pipeline fails to complete before the timeout, it will be cancelled and the error code will be set to DEADLINE_EXCEEDED. If unspecified, it will default to 7 days.
